content.rendered: Yosef Alemayehu Building Constructions Contractor PLC is a Building Contractor engaged in Building and Road Constructions projects with Governmental Offices & Medium to Large Enterprises. The owner wanted to create a Brand Identitiy framework that communicates the brand values in a clear and memorable way. This is the story of how that collaboration between me and the client yielded the brand framework with a refined presentation through YACON building contractor.
